  body
    include index

    .contact-hero
      h1 Contact Us

    .contact-content
      p If you have any questions, feedback, or just want to say hello, drop us a line at:
      p
        strong Email:
        a(href="mailto:support@savebytes.org") support@savebytes.org
      p
        strong Phone: +1 (555) 123-4567

      hr
      h2 Send Us a Message
      form.contact-form(action="/contact" method="POST")
        label(for="name") Your Name
        input#name(type="text" name="name" required)

        label(for="email") Your Email
        input#email(type="email" name="email" required)

        label(for="message") Message
        textarea#message(name="message" rows="6" required)

        button.btn.submit-btn(type="submit") Send Message